@elcantitocafe üáµüá∑ For a taste of Puerto Rico without needing to leave town, head to El Cantito Cafe. Located along Central Park Avenue in Yonkers, El Cantito Cafe is a no-frills eatery that offers authentic Puerto Rican cuisine in a cozy space perfect for enjoying a casual meal with friends or family. Their menu is filled with classic favorites prepared using traditional recipes, including empanadas, pollo en fricase (stewed chicken), churrasco (skirt steak), pernil asado (slow roasted pork), and a mofongo bar where your choice of protein is added to your choice of mofongo base. A small collection of beer and wine is available to accompany your meal, as well as refreshing soft drinks, and be sure to save room for their popular homemade cheese flan. Offering dine-in, takeout, delivery, and catering, El Cantito Cafe invites you to experience delicious Puerto Rican dining whenever the craving strikes.
